<span style="color:#00E447">═ᗌ ✎JeffTheJiller:</span> If you give it the right suggestions. Help it connect the dots, suddenly the apple is an orange.<br>
<span style="color:#00E447">═ᗌ ✎JeffTheJiller:</span> And once you know how to do it, suddenly reality becomes a lot less incomprehensible.<br>
